@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title Supply Purchase Order State Transition

[*] --> Draft : Purchase order created

Draft --> Submitted : Order finalized
Draft --> Cancelled : Order not needed

Submitted --> Confirmed : Supplier confirms
Submitted --> Rejected : Supplier rejects

Rejected --> Draft : Modify and resubmit
Rejected --> Cancelled : Order cancelled

Confirmed --> InTransit : Items shipped

InTransit --> Receiving : Delivery arrived

Receiving --> PartiallyReceived : Some items delivered
Receiving --> FullyReceived : All items delivered

PartiallyReceived --> FullyReceived : Remaining items received

FullyReceived --> Completed : Inventory updated\nPayment processed

Completed --> [*] : Transaction closed
Cancelled --> [*] : Order terminated

Draft : Being prepared
Draft : Can be edited
Draft : Not sent to supplier

Submitted : Sent to supplier
Submitted : Awaiting confirmation

InTransit : Items being shipped
InTransit : Expected delivery date set

Completed : All items received
Completed : Stock updated
Completed : Purchase finalized

@enduml
